00:19:01.460 --> 00:19:02.168
And I hugged him.

00:19:02.168 --> 00:19:04.320
And I told him that
I'd see him after work

00:19:04.320 --> 00:19:06.440
and that I'd see
him when I got home.

00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:09.330
And those are the last
words that was between us,

00:19:09.330 --> 00:19:11.360
the last smile that
was between us.

00:19:11.360 --> 00:19:13.390
And I thank God for that
because sometimes we

00:19:13.390 --> 00:19:16.620
argue with our children or are
you argue with your parents.

00:19:16.620 --> 00:19:18.340
Just think if that
was the last word

00:19:18.340 --> 00:19:20.630
you had with your loved ones.

00:19:20.630 --> 00:19:23.046
So when you go home
today, tonight,

00:19:23.046 --> 00:19:25.420
and during the holidays, and
you're with your loved ones,

00:19:25.420 --> 00:19:28.880
make sure those-- you
never know-- last words are

00:19:28.880 --> 00:19:32.910
great words, that love
is said between you,

00:19:32.910 --> 00:19:35.339
that all the things that are
little, minute new things,

00:19:35.339 --> 00:19:36.630
especially during the holidays.

00:19:36.630 --> 00:19:38.939
People have a sense of
this heightened things

00:19:38.939 --> 00:19:39.980
going during the holiday.

00:19:39.980 --> 00:19:42.600
That's why people argue a
lot during the holidays.

00:19:42.600 --> 00:19:44.350
People want to come
to certain homes,

00:19:44.350 --> 00:19:47.244
and they don't get there because
of certain things like traffic

00:19:47.244 --> 00:19:48.410
or whatever the case may be.

00:19:48.410 --> 00:19:51.080
And it's always the good and
the bad during the holidays.

00:19:51.080 --> 00:19:54.250
That's why there's so many
suicides during the holidays.

00:19:54.250 --> 00:19:57.030
