00:26:05.050 --> 00:26:08.330
they close many of their
cases with this same police

00:26:08.330 --> 00:26:09.870
department.

00:26:09.870 --> 00:26:12.240
So they're on a
friendly basis, and they

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:14.515
uplift the police
when they testify

00:26:14.515 --> 00:26:16.980
against other defendants.

00:26:16.980 --> 00:26:21.050
So I cannot uplift the policemen
and then tear them down later

00:26:21.050 --> 00:26:24.300
on when he commits an act such
as what happened with Freddie

00:26:24.300 --> 00:26:28.550
Gray because I've held
him up to a standard,

00:26:28.550 --> 00:26:32.500
and then I've closed 12,
13 cases with him or her.

00:26:32.500 --> 00:26:35.870
And then, all of a sudden
now, if I tear him down,

00:26:35.870 --> 00:26:38.400
we have to go back and
re-look at all those cases

00:26:38.400 --> 00:26:41.640
