system that we have,

00:27:02.530 --> 00:27:06.750
a defendant can get the best
defense that money can buy.

00:27:06.750 --> 00:27:08.150
Am I correct?

00:27:08.150 --> 00:27:09.664
Best defense that money can buy.

00:27:09.664 --> 00:27:11.080
If you're a
multi-millionaire, you

00:27:11.080 --> 00:27:15.230
can get a multimillion
dollar team of attorneys.

00:27:15.230 --> 00:27:18.130
But think about the
victim's family in our case.

00:27:18.130 --> 00:27:22.421
You are represented by the
prosecutor in that county.

00:27:22.421 --> 00:27:23.420
You don't have a choice.

00:27:23.420 --> 00:27:25.250
You can be a billionaire.

00:27:25.250 --> 00:27:26.870
You don't have a choice.

00:27:26.870 --> 00:27:28.200
You have to be represented.

00:27:28.200 --> 00:27:33.541
If the prosecutor
is a knucklehead,

00:27:33.541 --> 00:27:36.160
if the prosecutor is a
friend of the police,

00:27:36.160 --> 00:27:38.310
if the prosecutor is
a friend of the court,

00:27:38.310 --> 00:27:40.570
the prosecutor is a
friend of the city clerk,

00:27:40.570 --> 00:27:43.090
and he knows if he
prosecute this policeman,

00:27:43.090 --> 00:27:48.350
he may have the police end
up having to pay $5 million,

00:27:48.350 --> 00:27:52.860
like in Chicago to the
families, $10 million,

00:27:52.860 --> 00:27:55.640
the Garner family, all this.

00:27:55.640 --> 00:28:02.150
So they have invested reason
to acquit the police department

00:28:02.150 --> 00:28:03.470
when there's wrongdoing.

00:28:03.470 --> 00:28:05.610
The only reason
