00:29:08.630 --> 00:29:10.180
So we see that time
and time again.

00:29:10.180 --> 00:29:12.370
And the only way to
change it is to make sure

00:29:12.370 --> 00:29:15.320
that you get outside
representation for the victim's

00:29:15.320 --> 00:29:18.340
family and the victim and
not use the prosecutor

00:29:18.340 --> 00:29:21.115
in the same jurisdiction.

00:29:21.115 --> 00:29:21.990
TORRENCE BOONE: Lucy.

