00:30:19.990 --> 00:30:26.940
We need to be there talking
to the Chief Justices.

00:30:26.940 --> 00:30:29.850
We need to be there
talking to our legislators.

00:30:29.850 --> 00:30:32.690
We need to be there
in those systems that

00:30:32.690 --> 00:30:36.060
continue to extend
this kind of behavior

00:30:36.060 --> 00:30:37.630
towards people of color.

00:30:37.630 --> 00:30:41.230
We need to make
them accountable.

00:30:41.230 --> 00:30:45.980
It's not going to be enough to
rally in the street about it.

00:30:45.980 --> 00:30:50.330
It's not going to be enough to
talk about how horrible it is

00:30:50.330 --> 00:30:53.360
