going to do is talk about it.

00:31:06.210 --> 00:31:08.220
And all we'll
continue to do is talk

00:31:08.220 --> 00:31:10.980
about the next time it
happens, and the next time

00:31:10.980 --> 00:31:15.520
it happens, and gather, and talk
about it behind closed doors.

00:31:15.520 --> 00:31:21.970
So we have to be accountable
as a community of minorities,

00:31:21.970 --> 00:31:24.440
as a community in
urban communities,

00:31:24.440 --> 00:31:28.770
we have to be accountable
for making the change happen.

00:31:28.770 --> 00:31:33.880
We have to pressure the powers
that be to make these changes.

00:31:33.880 --> 00:31:36.910
We have to let them know that
they are accountable to us,

00:31:36.910 --> 00:31:39.470
and we will take
them out of office.

00:31:39.470 --> 00:31:42.190
When you go to the polls--
when you go, and you're

00:31:42.190 --> 00:31:47.050
voting for your local and civil
leaders at the local level,

00:31:47.050 --> 00:31:50.180
this is where all
of this happens.

00:31:50.180 --> 00:31:52.230
This is where all
of this happens.

00:31:52.230 --> 00:31:55.010
You have a responsibility
to go to the polls

00:31:55.010 --> 00:31:58.960
and to scream loudly and
clearly about what's happening.

00:31:58.960 --> 00:32:03.160
And if you don't, shame on you.

