01:27:10.920 --> 01:27:12.840
they do it to the black people.

01:27:12.840 --> 01:27:15.080
So you cannot let
them separate gender,

01:27:15.080 --> 01:27:17.440
separate sexual orientation.

01:27:17.440 --> 01:27:20.340
You can't let them
separate nationalities.

01:27:20.340 --> 01:27:22.650
When it's wrong, and
it's discrimination,

01:27:22.650 --> 01:27:25.380
you must find it
any and everywhere.

01:27:25.380 --> 01:27:29.870
LUCY MCBATH: And let me speak
from the mother's perspective,

01:27:29.870 --> 01:27:32.180
definitely speaking from
the mother's perspective.

01:27:32.180 --> 01:27:36.830
Yes, a mother's heart is what
the country usually hears.

01:27:36.830 --> 01:27:38.920
But, even in that,
there's stigmatism

01:27:38.920 --> 01:27:41.500
with the black mothers.

01:27:41.500 --> 01:27:46.290
We are vilified because
the country in the world

01:27:46.290 --> 01:27:49.900
says that you didn't
raise them properly.

01:27:49.900 --> 01:27:52.660
That's the reason why
they were gunned down

01:27:52.660 --> 01:27:54.890
because they were
in the wrong place

01:27:54.890 --> 01:27:56.930
at the wrong time
doing something wrong.

01:27:56.930 --> 01:28:01.970
It's automatically assumed
that they are in the wrong

01:28:01.970 --> 01:28:05.120
and that we are
not good mothers.

01:28:05.120 --> 01:28:07.520
We didn't raise them right.

01:28:07.520 --> 01:28:09.150
They didn't do the right thing.

01:28:09.150 --> 01:28:10.490
I didn't do the right thing.

01:28:10.490 --> 01:28:12.960
That's the reason why
they were gunned down.

01:28:12.960 --> 01:28:16.250
And, as a message to
your whole community,

01:28:16.250 --> 01:28:18.050
this is what will
continue to happen

01:28:18.050 --> 01:28:21.810
if you don't raise your voice
and raise your children right.

01:28:21.810 --> 01:28:24.310
So there's a stigma
on the mother.

01:28:24.310 --> 01:28:26.580
Even though you hear
the voice, we're

01:28:26.580 --> 01:28:31.030
still looked upon as
you didn't do it right,

01:28:31.030 --> 01:28:36.150
and you have no man
in the household.

01:28:36.150 --> 01:28:38.940
That's why you
didn't get it right.

01:28:38.940 --> 01:28:43.100
And where are the fathers,
as if to say that a mother,

01:28:43.100 --> 01:28:48.200
a strong black minority mother
cannot raise a strong black

01:28:48.200 --> 01:28:49.510
man.

01:28:49.510 --> 01:28:52.950
And that is a terrible misnomer.

01:28:52.950 --> 01:28:56.240
Most of the households in
this country that do not

01:28:56.240 --> 01:29:03.430
have fathers have very
strong, proud, educated, Godly

01:29:03.430 --> 01:29:08.240
black women that are
raising strong, educated,

01:29:08.240 --> 01:29:09.750
Godly black men.

01:29:09.750 --> 01:29:12.250
